configurationExportDTO Data Type

Contains the configuration data from an exported system

Note that v24 exports may contain exposure_vendors, exposure_departments and data_source properties, but those were never actually populated. We also no longer support them in v26+ (instead those values should get included as field values in the incident exposure_vendor_id, exposure_dept_id and data_source_ids fields). We ignore them on import.

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
action_order string element 0/unbounded The order of automatic actions being exported.
actions actionDTO element 0/unbounded The actions being exported. Contains both manual and automatic actions.
automatic_tasks automaticTaskDTO element 0/unbounded The automatic tasks being exported.
data_types (custom) element 0/1 The organization data types being exported.
export_date dateTime element 0/1 The date the configuration was exported.
export_format_version int element 0/1 The file format version number. If it's null, it means VERSION_1 because we didn't include it in the original release.
fields fieldDefDTO element 0/unbounded The fields being exported. Will contain any incident-specific fields as well as action-specific fields if actions were part of the export.
geos (custom) element 0/1 The organization geos being exported.
id int element 0/1 The internal ID of the exported configuration.
incident_artifact_types incidentArtifactTypeDTO element 0/unbounded The incident artifact types being exported.
incident_types incidentTypeDTO element 0/unbounded The incident types being exported.
industries (custom) element 0/1 The organization industries being exported.
layouts layoutDTO element 0/unbounded The layouts being exported. This includes the incident wizard, incident details view, incident close view.
message_destinations messageDestinationDTO element 0/unbounded The message destinations being exported.
notifications notificationDefDTO element 0/unbounded The notification definitions being exported.
overrides systemTaskOverrideDTO element 0/unbounded The system task overrides being exported.
phases phaseDTO element 0/unbounded The phases being exported.
regulators (custom) element 0/1 The organization regulators being exported.
scripts scriptDTO element 0/unbounded The scripts being exported.
server_version serverVersionDTO element 0/1 The version number from which the import was generated. If null, then it's a v24.x version that created it.
task_order string element 0/unbounded The task order being exported.
timeframes orgTimeframeDTO element 0/unbounded The organization timeframes being exported.
types typeDTO element 0/unbounded The custom types (currently only data tables) being exported.
workflows workflowDTO element 0/unbounded The workflows being exported
